messages.text: So there’s a problem.
What do you mean
I just hit someone with the car
WHAT
He was crossing the street in the dark
Did anyone see you?
No, I’m in the middle of nowhere
Is he dead?
He’s moaning, I think his legs are broken
Leave him and don’t call 911, they’ll trace you if he says what happened
I can’t just leave him
You have a job to do
Did he see your face?
Yes.
Shoot him and put him in the trunk for later.
There isn’t room in the trunk, because of the girl.
We need her by the time the full moon is fully risen
That’s in 30 minutes!!
He’s more awake, he’s begging for help
Why do you have a moral compass now
If you don’t do this you know what happens
Is the First Aid Kit still in the trunk?
Just shoot him!!
Fine I’ll look myself
I’m going to put him in the back and drop him at the hospital
Are you out of your mind??
We only need to kill the girl!
If I speed, I’ll get there
More people will die if you don’t bring this girl and you know it!
Dax??
DAX??
You better be on your way here!!
Are you fucking kidding me?? You’re his MOTHER??
Who is this??
Katherine. I managed to untie myself in the trunk, you bitch
I kicked your boy in his face, and he’s out cold on the ground
I called the police. They are on their way
You need to go in the car and lock yourself in it
Why would I do that?
You aren’t safe right now
And I was before?? I’m not doing a damn thing u say
Right now I’m going to stand here with my boy Pete
You both need to get in the car, or you are both going to die
You were going to kill me anyway!
Some sacrifice, he said while crying.
Like a total pussy.
Put him in the trunk and lock him in there
You only have 60 seconds
Lock you’re son in the trunk!? That’s rich.
Just do it!
Ur playing a trick on me
No I’m not, he’s going to turn
Turn into what!?
Just get in the car!!
What were u going 2 do 2 me??
You aren’t listening
Ur goddamn right I’m not you FREAK
Omg when u mean turned what did u mean
GET IN THE CAR!!!
I got in the car. What is going on????
What is he doing
He killed that guy
He tore out his neck with his teeth
Is he still feeding on him?
Yes
This can’t be real
This is why we needed you, so we could stop this from happening!
Check under the seat to see if there are extra keys
No
Okay, well now you have to just wait it out until the cops get there.
He will run, but now others’ deaths are on you!
The cops aren’t coming
There’s a warrant out for my arrest, so I never called
Did you call anyone??
He smashed my phone, I don’t remember any numbers
So there’s nobody on the way to shoot him?
He’s lunging at the car!!
Help me!!
His father would be upset, you know
I don’t care!
We’ve been keeping this at bay for ten years now.
Killing you would’ve given us another five
But there’s a ritual involved
You sick fucks!
The windshield cracked!
It’s been difficult on us. He doesn’t like the killing
HELP ME
If he gets in and tears you limb from limb, he’ll be destroyed
The window just cracked
Before I help you, do you know the song Black Bird?
What!?
It was a lullaby I used to sing him to sleep with
YES I KNOW IT HELP ME PLEASE
If you go below the passenger’s seat, there should be a gun there
The bullets are in the glove box
Try to aim for the heart
Let me know when it’s done
It’s done.
One shot?
Three. He’s still alive, but bleeding out
Will you please sing that song to him before he goes?
Please. I know you don’t understand.
Are you still there
Yes.
Please
Ok
Are you?
Yes
Now run as fast as you can
There are going to be more of them
If only you knew what you could’ve stopped
